{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1150420acf","title":"对《上海市税务机关征税中违反政策现象严重》一文的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b65cbac36","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":21,"articleId":"1150420acf"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"b4ee75b33d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这篇文章载于《人民日报》1953年3月18日编印的《党报通讯》第四期。文中说，上海市税务局自去年开展劳动竞赛以来，不断发生为“完成任务”、为“争取红旗”而预借货物税、营业税等严重违反政策的现象。商人们反映：“你们搞劳动竞赛是为了光荣，我们却要早付钱。”更严重的是有些税务局竞用侵犯人权的非法手段去强征税款。这种行为已引起商人极大不满，有的商人在市场上公开骂政府。"},{"id":"8a86df6244","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任兼财政部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"84c31bfe9a","type":"title","text":"对《上海市税务机关征税中违反政策现象严重》一文的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf"},{"id":"b4ee75b33d","type":"paragraph","text":"薄一波同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf"},{"id":"8a86df6244","type":"paragraph","text":"上海税务局应加整顿，对严重违法乱纪分子应作适当处置，争取主动，免被资本家告发，陷于被动。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf"},{"id":"8f7fc1bce8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf"},{"id":"5e2b4412de","type":"paragraph","text":"三月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf"}],"page":{"id":"46f6084d2b","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"1150420acf","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}